snippet.title: Your South Florida Lawyer, Patrick J. McGeehan
snippet.description:
I am your South Florida Lawyer, Patrick McGeehan! A lawyer is a lawyer, is a lawyer, they say. What sets your lawyer apart from all the other lawyers out there? I'll tell you what sets us apart, our level and type of service. I am the anti-lawyer lawyer.

The fact remains, we have a judicial system that most people cannot navigate yet alone understand.  Most people who are involved in family law matters and criminal matters, especially misdemeanors, cannot afford legal representation and must go it on their own.  Through this channel, I will explain legal concepts in these areas of law to help you navigate the system.  


The content on my site is for educational purposes and is not to be considered legal advice.  No attorney/client relationship is formed by any activities or exchanges herein.
